.SH "Detailed Description"
.PP 
Class to handle exception\&. 

Provides public functions to get the error number, error offset and error message\&.
.PP
Any exception should be caught by reference, e\&.g 
.PP
.nf
try {
    throw Except("Error", 1, 2);
}
catch( Except& e){
    std::cout<<e\&.what();
}

.fi
